cs.CV, cs.MM, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.GR 

The paper deals with face recognition, which is a common topic in computer vision (cs.CV). The use of deep learning techniques such as CNNs suggests that it could also fall under machine learning (cs.MM) and machine learning applications (cs.LG). The use of 3D reconstruction techniques could also suggest computer graphics (cs.GR). Finally, the paper's focus on recognition and classification could suggest artificial intelligence (cs.AI).
